=E2=80=9CBullish on crypto=E2=80=9D means that he has lots of crypto compan=
ies to=C2=A0<em>sue</em>, because their cryptocurrencies went down.</p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I am also bullish on crypto, for plaintiffs=E2=80=
=99 lawyers. For one thing it is pretty obvious that there are lots of larg=
